    "long_instructions": "##Text\r\nAdd a some text to your project!\r\n\r\n1. Snap `set heading` under when run\r\n\r\n2. Add `set subheading` below it\r\n\r\n3. Type your text!\r\n\r\nPress Run\r\n",
    "instructions_icon": "emoji",
